{"tid":797463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"制服配白色胸罩比較「不透」？　內衣廠證實學校錯了","createTime":"2018-08-28T13:57:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T14:02:55.000Z","uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1852ce9e79480dcbd0a4de38ed4e4385e1b356ff","tid":797463,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T13:57:19.000Z","msg":"日韓有許多學校規定，女學生穿制服時得搭配白色內衣，理由是因為穿相同顏色，這樣內衣才不會太明顯透出來，但事實卻好像並非如此！日本一內衣品牌就做了實驗，他們準備了白色、粉紅色、水藍色、皮膚色、紅色以及深藍色的色塊布料，放在膚色的背景上，再用白色的布料蓋上去，實驗看看哪種顏色會顯得最明顯。<br />\n<br />\n結果赫然發現，白色、粉紅色、水藍色等淺色系的色塊反而比深色區的紅色、深藍色更加明顯，讓該內衣廠在推特呼籲「希望讓大家改掉『白色＋白色比較不會透』的觀念！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/life/realtime/20180828/1419420\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flife%2Frealtime%2F20180828%2F1419420&d=qVLSHLgkGmWQNFq70Z9n5ROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=0c645d91\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flife%2Frealtime%2F20180828%2F1419420&h=553afd9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/life/realtime/20180828/1419420</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180828/640_f20ab1f555590d4acd14ac4107bc3358.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180828%2F640_f20ab1f555590d4acd14ac4107bc3358.jpg&h=11e2e9f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 方便阿sir揾食"},{"pid":"eda0b6306d58a1694f796cd9b16614e2aa2d24b2","tid":797463,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T14:02:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}